definition: down/downwards/below/lower/later/next (week etc)/second (of two parts)/to decline/to go down/to arrive at (a decision, conclusion etc)/measure word to show the frequency of an action

sentences.english: The Soyuz spacecraft appears at the bottom left.
sentences.chinese: 聯盟號宇宙飛船出現在圖片的左下方。

sentences.english: Aex beat enlargement and left-downward displacement.
sentences.chinese: 心尖搏動範圍擴大，向左下移位。

sentences.english: The attenuation weak spot is the black strip in the lower left corner of the band.
sentences.chinese: 天線的衰減弱點就是鋼圈左下角的黑色覆蓋物。

sentences.english: The vast majority of western medicine is down in this bottom left hand corner.
sentences.chinese: 大量的西藥都在置於手邊左下角。

sentences.english: The proton number is in the lower left corner.
Other features visible in the image include a solid field of low cloud cover at the lower left corner of the image.
sentences.chinese: 圖像中的其他可見特徵包括密佈於左下角的低雲。

sentences.english: In the bottom left corner of the figure, examples of small-scale institution-based initiatives are listed.
sentences.chinese: 在圖的左下角列出基於機構的小型舉措。

sentences.english: The building on the lower left is the main chapel.
sentences.chinese: 圖示浸信會建於礐石的會址，左下方爲該會禮拜堂。

sentences.english: In the lower left-hand corner, however, there's an anchor – and a dinner bell.
sentences.chinese: 在畫的左下角竟然畫了一隻錨和一隻喫飯鍾。

sentences.english: Remember to mark the position you apply on the left-down side of the envelop and cover of resume.

sentences.english: Donors are over here, the metals on the left end of the Periodic Table.

sentences.english: You'll see the connection in the lower left-hand side.

sentences.english: The association of horseshoe kidney with left inferior vena cava is rare.
sentences.chinese: 馬蹄型腎合併左下腔靜脈是相當罕見的病例。

sentences.english: The zoning page can be reached using the far right button in the group on the bottom lefthand corner of the window.
sentences.chinese: 使用窗口左下角最右側的按鈕可以訪問到分區頁面。

sentences.english: The Configuration view in the lower-left corner always displays the resulting contents of a method configuration.
sentences.chinese: 左下角的配置視圖總是顯示一個方法配置的結果內容。

sentences.english: We're going to begin in the lower left corner.
